Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Servant x Service Eps2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.02,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:05.12,Servant_Italics,,0,0,0,,ミヨシさん、いないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:09.50,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,ミヨシさん、何してるんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:11.32,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,あ、いや、あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:15.28,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,すみません。これには訳が、、、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.53,Servant_Main,Grandma,0,0,0,,いた、いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:21.04,Servant_Main,Grandma,0,0,0,,サヤちゃんもう聞いて頂戴。うちの嫁がね、、、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:56.66,Servant_Ep_Title,Title,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:55.99,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,{\a6}一度、お年寄りの方に捕まると
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:58.62,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,{\a6}数時間世間話になってしまい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:03.26,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,それで、凄く申し訳ないのですが、ちょっと隠れさせて頂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:06.14,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,でもかくれてたら事務仕事もできないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.34,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,ミヨシさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:10.02,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:13.36,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,イチミヤさん、ミヨシさんが凹んでしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.80,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,何とかして、先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.03,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,う、うん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:21.73,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,いや、ミヨシさんは新人としては、普通の部類に入ると思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.08,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,その調子です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.71,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,先輩、良い感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:28.21,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,ほ、本当？よし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.08,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,君はよくやっているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.58,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,今年の新人は凄いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:34.71,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,ヤマガミさんはバーとガーと要領よくできてるし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.72,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,ハサべに至っては、すでに、上司の俺より仕事できるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.18,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,イチミヤさんまで凹まないで下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:47.18,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,私のことですみなせん、皆さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.50,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,私もいい加減ちゃんとしないといけませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.65,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,あ、あ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.32,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,はい、もしもし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:56.68,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,はい、分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.57,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,ミヨシさん、大丈夫でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:04.38,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,まあ、同じ新人でどうせのルーシーがバリバリ働いていて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.75,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,プレッシャーなんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.29,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,そんなつもりはないんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.91,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,つもりはなくてもさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:15.92,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,そうだ。なんか私もまだまだ的なアッピールをさり気なくしたら？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.88,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,例えば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.08,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,そうだな。書類ぶちまけて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.88,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,「キャー、ルーシードジしちゃった」とかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.38,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,あっ、あは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:28.39,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,それでも、「ルーシーこんな難しいことできません」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:31.69,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,「助けて、ハセベ様」とか言ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.35,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,それは死んでも断ります
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.60,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,ルーシーは薄情だな。ミヨシちゃんのためだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.74,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,あっ、分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.68,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,ど、ドジちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.95,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,ちょっ、ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.74,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,写メ撮らないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.20,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,安心しろ、ムービーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.62,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,むしはもっと安心できません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.54,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,ちょっちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.67,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,ハセベさんじゃ相談にならないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.76,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,そうだ。チハヤさんに相談してみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.65,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,あのう、チハヤさん、ちょっといいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:14.19,Three Rules,Lucy,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.32,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,えっ、あの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.19,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,ヤマガミさん、どうしました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:17.65,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,なるほど、それは確かに心配ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.42,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,私も少し考えておきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:22.15,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.24,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,それはそうと、ヤマガミさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.61,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,明日用事があって休むので
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.28,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,私の仕事色々お願いして良いですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.45,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,はい、分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.08,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,何の用事ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.96,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,なんか楽しそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:41.68,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,今日はミヨシさん大丈夫かな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.20,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,いや、ミヨシさんの事も大したけど、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.00,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,今日はいないチハヤさんの分も頑張らないと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.72,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,ヤマガミさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.81,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,あれ、チハヤっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.85,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,チっ、チハヤさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:54.83,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,どうしたんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.86,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,倉庫のかぎ間違って持って帰ちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.11,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,使うだろうから渡しておきます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.53,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,あの、ええとですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.34,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.36,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,待って、何があったんですか、チハヤさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.37,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,チハヤじゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.91,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,マジカルフラワーガーベラピンクよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.71,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:21.34,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,いいえ、あの、用事ってこれだったんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:26.68,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,はい、本当はマナー違反なのですが会場がここから近かった物で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:30.71,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,レイヤーんの集まるとかイベントって結構あるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:36.04,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,だから私、コスプレ続けるために、休みの取りやすい臨時職員なんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.35,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Temporary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:43.89,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,That's right. I didn't take the civil \Nservant's test, so my term is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:46.82,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I'm pretty much an "irregular" staff member.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.66,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,When you say "irregular" \Nlooking like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.33,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,it takes on an entirely \Ndifferent connotation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.70,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Long live temp employees!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.89,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Are you interested in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.42,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,No... it's just that I've never \Nseen a book like that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.43,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,If you'd like, I'll let you borrow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.73,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.18,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,So, this is like where you make \Nyour own book to sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.60,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,I've seen that on TV before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:28.07,Doki Doki Flowers,Chihaya,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,400)}Doki Doki Flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.16,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,It's something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.74,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,A lot of civil servants make doujinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.92,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,We easily get vacation time \Nfor Obon and New Year's,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.61,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,so this country definitely supports otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:31.12,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,I feel like this country \Nhas some issues, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.97,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Oh, what is this? A Manga Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.64,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I'll clean this up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.87,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,It's okay. Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.58,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Is this what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.67,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:42.67,Servant_Italics,Character,0,0,0,,{\a6}Itemaiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:46.67,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,it's an anime currently popular \Nwith girls called {\i1}Magical Flowers{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.17,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.49,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,I know that title. \NIt's also a game, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.91,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Wow, you know quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.14,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Yeah, I play lots of games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.11,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,FF, DQ, Pokimon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:02.60,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Mariko Kart, Dokimemo, \NAER, Fete, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:06.24,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,You play all kinds, \Nnot that I'm familiar with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.21,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,I play everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.07,Servant_Italics,Chihaya,0,0,0,,There were some adult titles in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.82,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.72,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.45,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Civil servants aren't allowed \Nto dress flamboyantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.01,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,so is that a bit frustrating for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.25,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Cosplay isn't only about being flamboyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.46,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,For example, this is a civil \Nservant cosplay for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.46,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Civil servant cosplay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.11,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Nurses and office ladies are \Na part of cosplay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.26,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,So in a way, Yamagami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.72,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,you're doing a civil servant \Ncosplay, too, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.97,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:39.47,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,I feel embarrassed all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.48,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Then take off your clothes and \Nstop doing cosplay right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.37,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.93,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.75,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.93,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,You weren't fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.40,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:55.66,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Even putting cosplay aside, \Nyou dress quite plainly, Yamagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:08:00.57,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Oh... Well, I'm not really \Nall that interested in clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.97,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,I think black is generic, so it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.25,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Black... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.50,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Even if I got into fashion, \NI wouldn't look good in anything I wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.49,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Even these clothes are a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.90,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Since they're a waste, take 'em off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.76,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.06,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Yes, regarding that matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.89,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Then, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.56,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.31,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.97,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Yamagami-san, is it really not that \Nyou aren't interested in clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.98,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,but that you can't find the \Nclothes that fit you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.57,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Because of your breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:41.95,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,No! Mine might be big for my height \Nbut they're nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:43.85,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,F cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.67,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,D-Do they look that small?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.59,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.55,Servant_Italics,Chihaya,0,0,0,,F is small? What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.51,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Anyway... clothes are \Nimportant for professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.85,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,You have to give them more thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.97,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.13,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,So, Yamagami-san, let's do \Nsome anime character cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.48,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:11.57,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Once you experience it, \Nyou can wear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.49,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,That's too much experience for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:18.81,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I always thought you would \Nlook good as Rose Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.11,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,R-Rose Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.41,Magical Flowers,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1)}Magical Flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.41,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,She's a friend of Gerbera Pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.66,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,N-No way! I couldn't wear such an outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.36,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:30.26,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Rose Black represents black, \Nas her name suggests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:33.97,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,The safe, generic black, like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.13,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Even though this one \Nshows the most skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:45.10,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Black might be okay... but \Nplease, let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.74,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:49.64,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I know about clothes \Nmore than most people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:52.35,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,so please, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:59.20,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I love seeing people enjoying \Nclothes, myself included.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:03.04,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I would love to see \Nyou enjoying fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.03,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.14,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,I-I will try to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.21,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I look forward to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.42,Servant_Italics,,0,0,0,,Seeing you as Rose Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.23,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san... \Nis a such nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.89,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.80,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,You can't just... I-I mean, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.41,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.82,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Were you scolded, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.50,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Did some of our citizens scold you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.01,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,She's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.57,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Everyone... prepare yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.25,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,The nuisance is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.03,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.54,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,You call me, a law abiding \Ncitizen, a nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.26,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,You public servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.14,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,It's a high school girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.97,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,It is a high school girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.21,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,She's a high school girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.76,Servant_Main,Worker (guy),0,0,0,,That's Toko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:55.63,Servant_Main,Worker (girl),0,0,0,,Toko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.13,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,S-Sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.96,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,So, Senpai, who is this \Nhigh school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.83,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,She's a regular here... \Na health welfare nut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.00,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}not{\i0} a nut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.69,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.92,Servant_Main,Yoko,0,0,0,,I've been coming here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.23,Servant_Main,Yoko,0,0,0,,to do the health and welfare \Npaperwork for my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:14.94,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Memorizing welfare laws is my hobby. \NNice to meet you folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.12,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Now I will administer a test \Nfor you new employees
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:24.03,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,to see if you were able \Ncapable of your jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.66,Servant_Main,Lucy; Miyoshi; Hasebe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.25,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,U-Um... Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.87,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Because I'll be in trouble if \Nyou can't do your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.29,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,What did you mean by "test"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.12,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,I'll just have you act like \Nyou're at the customer counter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.71,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,and I'll see if you can\N properly do the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.84,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,A little too much time \Non your hands, Toko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.67,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm offering to ascertain if you're
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.26,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,able to serve the citizens as a \Nlegitimate civil servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.72,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it. Let's do the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:51.16,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,T-Try not to provoke her too much, she's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.19,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.53,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,She knows way more than most professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.60,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,So if you're not on your guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.44,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,By the way, since
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.54,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,you confused "nursing senior welfare facility" \Nand "nursing senior insurance facility,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.30,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,how can you be expected\N to teach the newcomers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.32,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? \NAre you just going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:08.31,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,As you can see, she rips apart your soul, \Nso you have to be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.83,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ichimiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.79,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Then I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.50,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,So you're going first? Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.00,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Toko-chan, which high school do you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.01,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Which year are you in? \NDo you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.09,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have a lot of friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.80,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Will you introduce them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.97,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Wait a sec! Let me speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.18,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Why are you making her mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.13,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:32.06,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,If I can answer your question,\Ngive me your email address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.87,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.14,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Come on, is it a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:39.02,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Okay, but if you get it wrong, \Nyou'd better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.03,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.90,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,What is article 78 section 7 \Nof the nursing insurance law?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:47.09,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,As designated by article 42 \Nsection 2's first clause,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.32,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,a person conducting business related to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.88,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,senior nursing living facilities \Nand their caregivers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:55.87,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,may resign from the position with at least one month's prior notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.26,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,I got a high school girl's email address!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.73,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell if he's smart \Nor just plain dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.80,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,N-Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.07,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,All right, you're next. \NYou will do the simulation test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.26,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,O-Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:12.45,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Pretend that I'm a client \Nthat came to your counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:17.06,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Well... then please \Nfill out this form...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:20.85,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Um, please don't get too angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.85,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,If you don't do anything weird, \NI won't get mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.36,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,If you scold me... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.41,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,I said I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.82,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,U-Um, uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.57,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.77,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you make yourself \Na little more clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.67,Servant_Main,Grandma,0,0,0,,Why're you being so mean to Saya-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:39.37,Tanaka_13:36,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san (76)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.38,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.87,Servant_Main,Grandma,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.94,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, you're wearing \Nsuch a short skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.24,Servant_Main,Grandma,0,0,0,,What will you do if your \Nlower body gets cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:50.55,Servant_Main,Grandma,0,0,0,,{\a6}My son's wife is just like you, \Nshowing off her legs... I'm so ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:50.55,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Um... Please don't be so mad at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.77,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:57.08,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... \NWell, I'll do my best, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.75,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,You seem normal. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.32,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:05.28,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Your name. I wouldn't \Nmind remembering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:12.28,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Y-Yamagami Lucy Kimiko Akie \NAiri Shiori Rinne Yoshiho—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.04,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.75,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Jeez! What's with \Nthis year's newcomers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.08,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Hitting on a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.92,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,summoning an old lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.63,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,having some ridiculous name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.54,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,You'd better educate them properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:26.38,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,C-Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:30.34,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,At this rate, you're going to disturb everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:34.89,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,She hugged him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.52,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Calm down, Toko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.48,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Calling a high school girl \Nby just her first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.29,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Here you go, Toko, a welfare guide...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.30,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,I have this month's newsletter, too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.95,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Ooh! I'll read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.57,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,I'll give you some allowance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.16,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,so go get some cake \Nand read it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.44,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.98,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,He gave her money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.71,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,He gave money to a high school girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.58,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:06.38,Servant_Italics,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Crap! Both the citizens and my \Nprotégés are giving me an icy stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:10.22,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,He was hugged by a high school \Ngirl and even gave her money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.17,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Ichimiya-san, you're so vulgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.07,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,No! I'm her—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.17,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Toko Ichimiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.44,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Oh, this is the application \Nform from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.81,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,That girl's last name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.25,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Toko Ichimiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.66,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Ichimiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.57,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,I'm her unreliable brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.57,Servant_Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.86,Servant_Main,Civilian,0,0,0,,Oh, they're just brother and sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.00,Servant_Main,Civilian,0,0,0,,Causing a scene like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:41.70,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,People tell us that \Nwe don't look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:45.04,Servant_Main,Hasebe,0,0,0,,Senpai, why did Toko-chan \Nturn out that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.32,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,She wasn't always like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.77,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,Hurry up with my snack! \NGive it to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.12,Servant_Flashback,,0,0,0,,You suck at doing my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.72,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:57.23,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Sorry, she's always been like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.22,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Ichimiya-san, you apologize too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:03.60,Servant_Main,Ichmiya,0,0,0,,The reason she became interested \Nin the ward office was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.58,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, what's that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:09.77,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a ward office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:12.49,Servant_Flashback,,0,0,0,,That's where they help \Npeople who are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:16.20,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,They help people in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.38,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.16,Servant_Flashback,,0,0,0,,they consult with you \Non various issues, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.75,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, \NI'm considering working there, Toko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:33.51,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,While I'm at work, you'll be home alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.51,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,but you're responsible and \Nyou'll be okay on your own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.69,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Besides, you don't like me all that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.75,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's better if I'm not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.33,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,A few days after I said that to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:47.77,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:52.20,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home, Toko. \NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.21,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,I was at the ward office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.74,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,The ward office? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:59.20,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,People at the Health and Welfare \NDivision taught me a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.67,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,Apparently, we can get \Nquite a bit of money
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:04.16,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,if we ask for mother \Nand child assistance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.01,Servant_Flashback,,0,0,0,,or high-priced medical \Nor nursing services...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.46,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,But we haven't applied for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.38,Servant_Flashback,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:12.03,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.84,Servant_Flashback,Ichmiya,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.21,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,You're only gonna make \Nchump change working part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.40,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,You need to become a civil servant \Nright after high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:21.42,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,It's a good, reasonable job because \Nthe income and work hours are steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.81,Servant_Flashback,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:27.31,Servant_Flashback,Toko,0,0,0,,S-So you stay home and study!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:31.28,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Ever since then, she's loved \Nthe ward office...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.43,Servant_Italics,Lucy and Miyoshi,0,0,0,,No... it's not the ward office she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:38.24,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,I came for you again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.05,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,What happened to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.95,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,I was bored, so I just stopped by!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:47.46,Servant_Italics,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,So it's not about the ward office \Nor the welfare matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.38,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Hey! Why are you staring off into space?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.63,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Oh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.42,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,You make your living off of our \Ntax money, so get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:57.84,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,You're causing problems for the people and your senpai, who's my bro—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.15,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.31,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,You like your brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.92,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Hey! You think it's funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.42,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.00,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,You're working right now, \Nso get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.95,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Come on, Toko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.11,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:17.06,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,this does affect the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:22.37,Lunch_Break_Meeting_18:16,(Text),0,0,0,,Lunch Break Special Meeting\N\N\N\N\NWhat to do about Miyoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.72,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,So we're going to have a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.48,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,A random meeting has begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:27.04,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Some clients request \Nthe impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.82,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,so you have to learn to draw the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:35.21,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,I know, but I tend to say too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:38.76,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,so now I have a habit of \Nholding back what I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:40.97,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.45,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Since you want to change \Nyourself, you should try
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.77,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,"Blue Hydrangea" cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.27,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san, leave the \Ncosplay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:52.15,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Then this calls for drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.61,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Drastic measures?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:00.49,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,If that's the case, \NI wouldn't mind cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.28,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Toko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:07.10,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, because in the end, \Nit's for your beloved brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.50,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.54,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Do you think it will work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.38,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,She'll be fine. She won't \Nbe easily discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:20.26,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Well, give it to me straight, \Nwhat's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.59,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.96,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:27.88,Servant_Italics,,0,0,0,,What if she gets \Nmad or I hurt her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:31.60,Servant_Italics,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,But she said she'd cooperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.81,Servant_Italics,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.11,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.61,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,She got mad before she said anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.82,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Don't you have any pride? \NDon't you have anything to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:44.38,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Miyoshi-san, do it! \NJust say a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:48.83,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,She's right. Like, "You're just causing \Ntrouble, so leave, Tsundere."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:51.06,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Shut up, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.66,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Um, Toko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:53.33,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.67,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,I learn a lot when you \Ncome to the ward office a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:02.93,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,and I don't mind, but it's \Nkind of a waste of your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:06.06,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,because by doing this, your brother will \Nnever understand your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.62,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:12.30,Servant_Main,Civilian,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.07,Servant_Main,Civilian,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:13.81,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Toko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.42,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.39,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Miyoshi... She...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:19.98,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,What did Miyoshi-san do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.76,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Just now... she...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.32,Black_Text_20:19,,0,0,0,,There's No Way She Can Say It
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:27.81,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Damn it! Apologize! \NApologize to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.04,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.97,Servant_Italics,Lucy,0,0,0,,She's taking her anger \Nout on her brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:34.65,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,She's perfect for Hydrangea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.80,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san, even now you're \Ntalking about cosplay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:44.14,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,No, because hydrangea... \Nits flower meaning is "brutal."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.55,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Come on, Toko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.85,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.17,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,You're being a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:56.77,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Because of you, Miyoshi-san \Ncannot do her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.94,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Go home and watch the house, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.90,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go... I'm not \Ncoming back anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.24,Servant_Main,Ichimiya,0,0,0,,Atta girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.74,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,You finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.20,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,I kind of feel sorry for Toko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.71,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Miyoshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.35,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,Wait, Toko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:18.00,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,You give me lots of \Nvaluable information,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:21.28,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,so please continue to educate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.83,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,You can come anytime you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.97,Servant_Main,Miyoshi,0,0,0,,P-Perhaps every second \Nor third day, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.58,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,Y-You've got some nerve, Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.82,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,B-But if you insist, \NI guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.38,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,I will come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:41.19,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll work you to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.44,Servant_Main,Toko,0,0,0,,So you'd better be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.40,Servant_Main,Lucy,0,0,0,,Miyoshi-san is such a nice person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:49.81,Servant_Main,Chihaya,0,0,0,,But again, it doesn't help her \Nfocus on the task at hand, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:39.73,Quiz_text_23:24,,0,0,0,,Picture: Nakahara Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:28.71,Servant_Main,NA,0,0,0,,U-Um... it's time for this \Nweek's Servant Quiz again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:33.79,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Our ward office is in Hokkaido, but out of \NHokkaido, Honshu, Shikoku, Kyushu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:37.25,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,which island uses the most shouyu (soy sauce)?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:38.78,Servant_Main,,0,0,0,,Find out the answer on our website!
